terms: This Agreement and the Security Interests shall terminate on the date on which all payments under the Debentures have been indefeasibly paid in full and all other Obligations have been paid or discharged.
conditions: The terms and provisions of this Agreement are expressly conditioned upon, and subject to, the closing of the IPO Transactions.
